00:00:38,900 --> 00:00:41,820
=Episode 12=

11
00:00:42,320 --> 00:00:43,320
The throne and you,

12
00:00:43,320 --> 00:00:45,240
I want them all.

13
00:00:54,799 --> 00:00:55,759
Your Highness,

14
00:00:56,159 --> 00:00:57,320
why did you do this?

15
00:01:02,560 --> 00:01:03,600
Simple.

16
00:01:06,159 --> 00:01:07,640
I've fallen for you.

17
00:01:13,239 --> 00:01:15,079
Since you've laid it bare,

18
00:01:16,799 --> 00:01:18,239
I'll be honest too.

19
00:01:19,599 --> 00:01:20,840
Do you know

20
00:01:21,359 --> 00:01:22,680
why I broke into

21
00:01:23,439 --> 00:01:25,000
the Deathsworn Selection that day

22
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:26,400
and chose that path of certain death?

23
00:01:27,239 --> 00:01:28,319
And do you know

24
00:01:28,599 --> 00:01:30,079
why I chose you of all people?

25
00:01:31,079 --> 00:01:32,120
Ten years ago,

26
00:01:33,359 --> 00:01:34,519
Murong Xuanlie tortured

27
00:01:35,040 --> 00:01:36,879
my parents to death with his own hands.

28
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:38,959
I trained in the Shadow Bureau

29
00:01:39,200 --> 00:01:41,280
just to get close to him one day.

30
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:44,280
And you were the stepping stone I chose.

31
00:01:46,599 --> 00:01:47,400
So,

32
00:01:48,599 --> 00:01:49,840
from the very start,

33
00:01:49,840 --> 00:01:51,719
I was only your pawn.

34
00:01:52,840 --> 00:01:53,640
Yes.

35
00:01:54,239 --> 00:01:55,560
Your affections

36
00:01:56,079 --> 00:01:57,200
mean nothing to me.

37
00:02:01,040 --> 00:02:02,879
I can help you get revenge,

38
00:02:03,599 --> 00:02:05,640
as long as you stay by my side forever.

39
00:02:09,280 --> 00:02:10,439
My vengeance

40
00:02:11,439 --> 00:02:12,439
is mine to claim.

41
00:02:13,280 --> 00:02:15,080
I trust only the blade in my own hand.

42
00:02:15,599 --> 00:02:16,879
If anyone stands in my way,

43
00:02:17,560 --> 00:02:19,319
I won't show any mercy!

44
00:02:20,080 --> 00:02:21,719
Are you threatening me?

45
00:02:28,620 --> 00:02:30,580
ظآزMoonlight spills like quiet tidesظآز

46
00:02:30,830 --> 00:02:33,800
