63
00:03:34,759 --> 00:03:36,360
I promised I'd let you go.

64
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:37,919
So today,

65
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:43,319
I'll see you off as your brother would.

66
00:03:57,919 --> 00:03:59,360
One stroke of the comb,

67
00:04:00,719 --> 00:04:02,360
