70
00:04:25,439 --> 00:04:29,519
Only a prince's principal consort
may wear the Phoenix Hairpin.

71
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:31,560
Today,

72
00:04:31,839 --> 00:04:33,240
I give it to you.

73
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:37,279
Your Highness...

74
00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:39,399
I don't deserve this.

75
00:04:42,360 --> 00:04:43,199
Besides you,

76
00:04:44,399 --> 00:04:46,439
I'd give it to no one else.

77
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:53,120
Princess Anhe,

78
00:04:55,279 --> 00:04:56,399
