in the first place?

81
00:05:41,879 --> 00:05:44,839
I will never let her
marry Murong Xuanlie.

82
00:05:47,759 --> 00:05:48,680
Then,

83
00:05:49,680 --> 00:05:50,879
I'll wait and see.

